#: ../../tips_and_tricks/scopes/vectorscope_working.rst:44
msgid ""
"The next scope (after the :ref:`Histogram <scopes-histogram_working>` and "
"the :ref:`Waveform and RGB Parade <scopes-waveform_and_rgb_parade>`) we want "
